      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require certain individuals employed by the Federal Government to give 30 days written notice to the Committees on Appropriations of the House of Representatives and the Senate for certain obligations or expenditures over $5,000 to furnish or redecorate the office of such individual, and for other purposes.</title>
